@startuml 1G_Fan_Account_Profile_Address
title 1-G · Fan Account, Profile & Address Management (UC-F03 to UC-F06)

start
|Registered Fan|
if (Fan action?) then (Logout)
  :Click Logout;
  |System|
  :Revoke or expire bearer token;
  :Return to public fansite;
elseif (Fan action?) then (Reset Password)
  :Request password reset by email;
  |System|
  :Validate email within tenant scope;
  :Create reset token and send email;
  |Registered Fan|
  :Open reset link and enter new password;
  |System|
  :Validate token and update password hash;
elseif (Fan action?) then (Update Profile)
  :Edit username, display name,\navatar or profile information;
  |System|
  :Validate fields and uniqueness within tenant;
  :Save Fan profile changes;
else (Manage Addresses)
  :Add, edit, delete or set default address;
  |System|
  :Validate receiver name, phone,\naddress fields and tenant ownership;
  :Save FanAddress record;
endif

stop
@enduml
